lines.text: [last lines & Closing Credits Music starts, after robot disguised as a rabbit explodes]

lines.character: Yosemite Sam From Outer Space's Commander

lines.text: [Bugs chuckles, after hearing the explosion, on the radio]
Gee, I wonder if Amos n' Andy is on yet?
[Bugs chuckles, after hearing explosion then Closing Credits' music begins]
